						               													<description>Part of a three in one games system, MAG-Miners is a magnetic spaceship, flicking game for 1-2 players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In solo mode, you will be in charge of a fledgling, asteroid mining company. You will try to blow up asteroids, collect the valuable metal ore inside and transport it back to Earth, all on a very limited fuel (flick) budget.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As you start to turn a profit, you will be able to afford more fuel  for each mining trip. With enough wealth you will eventually unlock new ships to help you take out giant, ore encrusted asteroids in search of the fabled rare metals that will make you all filthy rich!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At any point during your solo campaign (or as a stand alone, heads up match), another player can take control of a band of raiders (with their own custom ships) and try to steal the miners ore and potentially capture their ships.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;I am hoping this game could evolve with expansions full of new ships for the miners and raiders alike, along with even bigger asteroids to truly take mining operations to be next level.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
